{"id":7344,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2004-08-07T22:57:41.000Z","cooked":"<p>Well I met a guy on the ICQ, who is from South Korea, from Gwangju (or how is it spelled), and who started to make a Korean translation for LBA 2 :eek:, but he didnt know, where to find suitable programs. I sent him my WinHQR and N-SoftInds LBA Text File Editor, and made him a font (which Im going to publicly release tomorrow). There was only one problem: that for complete Korean, LBA 2 would have to be Unicode or at least DBCS version, so the translation will be in Hangul Jamo.</p>\n<p>As evidence, I attached some screenshots, of what so far has been translated (3 in-game and 1 menu screenshots, tested on lbaguy3ds older version of LBA :-/). <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/wink.png?v=12\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":wink:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"posts_count":10,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T15:21:54.476Z","reply_count":8,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":7,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":75.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":7341,"topic_slug":"korean-lba-2","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Well... I met a guy on the ICQ, who is from South Korea, from Gwangju (or how is it spelled), and who started to make a Korean translation for LBA 2 :eek:, but he didn't know, where to find suitable programs. I sent him my WinHQR and N-SoftInd's LBA Text File Editor, and made him a font (which I'm going to publicly release tomorrow). There was only one problem: that for complete Korean, LBA 2 would have to be Unicode or at least DBCS version, so the translation will be in Hangul Jamo.\n \nAs evidence, I attached some screenshots, of what so far has been translated (3 in-game and 1 menu screenshots, tested on lbaguy3d's older version of LBA :-/). ;)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/korean-lba-2/7341/1","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null,"can_vote":false}
